4th May 2007: Version 2.0.1 released (first public release).

20th August 2007: Version 2.0.2 released.
	This release fixes some bugs relating to timeout guards in Alternatives, repeated channel guards in Alternatives, and fixes a few
	missing function implementations as well as mistakes relating to the Run methods.

5th November 2007: Version 2.0.3 released.
	This release avoids using the ebx/rbx register in the atomic code to avoid some portability problems, and properly adds support for Mac OS X.
